-- Airbus Unions Will Hamper Toulouse Output Until April 30, Les Echos Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-04-27T04:52:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/airbus-unions-will-hamper-toulouse-output-until-april-30-les-echos-says.html

          
          
             Airbus SAS unions will hamper
production at Toulouse until April 30 by preventing delivery of
plane sections in support of their demand for a pay rise of 3.5
percent, French daily Les Echos said, without citing anyone.  
 The unions have rejected an offer of 1.9 percent, according
to the newspaper. The Toulouse factory wonâ€™t be completely
blocked by the action, Les Echos cited an unidentified spokesman
as saying.  
          
          


  


        